{"tid":1017130,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"擁有能力者爸爸或媽媽的KPOP女！","createTime":"2019-02-11T08:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:53:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9e72b0fc75888ef85473b55f3d86f8d80cfaf7","tid":1017130,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p1-news.yamedia.tw/MjY4ODEzODNuZXdz/75256e835098bcca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1-news.yamedia.tw%2FMjY4ODEzODNuZXdz%2F75256e835098bcca.jpg&h=c8bd5cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrot歌手洪真英的父親是朝鮮大學經濟學的名譽教授，也是銀行常任監視委員，洪真英之前曾在綜藝節目上提到父親在她小時候的時候，都會把錢包打開跟她說想拿多少零用錢自己拿。<br />\n<br />\n睇IKON班MK仔上佢屋企好似唔係特別豪華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lht6-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/2dff6f0f8f30f61a955d1c6621687291/5CE45C22/t51.2885-15/e35/49505758_2227049337548656_8470451380673435739_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lht6-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;se=7&amp;ig_cache_key=MTk2ODQxMzk5ODQ0MzM0MDE1NQ%3D%3D.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lht6-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F2dff6f0f8f30f61a955d1c6621687291%2F5CE45C22%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F49505758_2227049337548656_8470451380673435739_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lht6-1.cdninstagram.com%26se%3D7%26ig_cache_key%3DMTk2ODQxMzk5ODQ0MzM0MDE1NQ%253D%253D.2&h=37927d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGFRIEND的成員Umji的父親是韓國知名的牙科醫院長，營運的牙醫在首爾有9間、仁川9間、京畿道有12間&hellip;&hellip;等，在韓國總共約有45間，Umji曾在綜藝節目中說小時候和爸爸一起去北韓醫療服務。<br />\n<br />\n45間...7仔咁開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/l038cckudh801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fl038cckudh801.jpg&h=d7c01443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE的成員Mina的父親是一位有名的整形外科醫師，是拍攝日本版《白色巨塔》時做為背景的大阪大學的醫學部所屬，也是醫療開發部的中心長。"},{"pid":"178514aeec776611d7bc95ea294149ac6